ActDefence Production Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Schedule to the Defence Production Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE DEFENCE PRODUCTION ACT in order to reduce the number of controlled goods and technologies to only those that are strategically significant to Canada or that pose national security concerns.
